Be2 O-O 8. O-O a5
{ As usual d6 is good alternative transposing to traditional Dragon but let's keep it in independent territory. }
9. a4 { The only way to stop ...a4. } 9... Nb4
{ Preparing ...d5 and there's not much White can do about it. } 10. Bg5
