5. Nc3 Bg7 6. Be3 Nf6 7. f3
{ A very common mistake. White plays as if it was a traditional Dragon and f3 is important move in the 'Yugoslav Attack'. However in the Accelerated Dragon Black is virtually a tempo ahead and can strike in the center first. I believe Black already takes over the initiative ! }
