{ Immediate e5 is well met by 15. h6 ! with big advantage in N.Firman - P. Nguyen, Krakow 2015. }
15. Bxf6 exf6 16. Ne2 Ra5
{ The most popular choice in correspondence games. 16. ..f5 is mostly played in over the board games and should be also fine. }
