20. Rd1 fxg4 21. axb4 Rxd5
{ nice exchange sacrifice. The Bishop was the only strong piece White had. Now Black is left with powerful Bishop pair and White's King can't feel safe. }
22. Qxd5 gxf3 23. Nd4 Qf6
{ I wouldn't like to play with such exposed King in a practical game. J. Duran Vallverdu - F.Ruiz-Jarabo, ICCF 2012 }
