Qxd4 Bg7 9. Bg5 O-O 10. Qd2 a5
{ would be very similar to 9. Be3 lines. In some cases the Bishop may be a bit loose on g5 and g1-a7 diagonal looks more important but on the other hand sometimes there will be some pressure on e7 pawn. }
