1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 g6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nc6
{ Bg7 is of course playable but then Black can't play 'Gurgenidze System' in the Maroczy Bind which is part of this repertoire. }
5. c4
{ Entering so called Maroczy Bind setup which isn't possible in traditional Dragon but we have to learn it. This is the price we pay for choosing this move order. }
5... Nf6 6. Nc3 d6 7. Be2 { Of course 7. Be3 would be innacurate due to Ng4. }
