{ very nice resource as pointed out by Greet. Black is happy to exchange Queens and is not afraid to damage the structure due to dynamic possibilities. }
12. Qxb6
{ Spoiling Black's structure but White's pieces are not coordinated and Black develops very dynamic play quickly }
12... axb6 13. Rac1 Rfc8 14. b3 b5
{ key move after which Black takes over the initiative. } *

