{ with typical endgame where Black has nothing to fear and if White tries something too active like }
20. g4 { then } 20... Bd7 21. Kf2 Ne6
{ and I prefer Black who has better control over dark squares. N.Short - D. Vocaturo, Helsingor 2017 }
