{ Black's Bishop pair fully compensates weak pawn on d6. } 15. O-O Be6 16. b3
{ 16. Nb5 Bxb2 can't be bad for Black. } 16... axb3 17. axb3 Re8 18. Qc1 Qa5
{ with active play in A.Mista - D. Kanovsky, Czechia 2012 } *

